# Riley source-reallocation decision matrix. trueROAS = (revenueCents / 100) / spend.
# Per-source floor: received >= 10 AND booked >= 3 on BOTH sides. Account scale floor:
# clicks >= 30, conversions >= 3, days >= 7. Meaningful difference: best >= 2x worst trueROAS.
